The Department of Natural Resources thru the Bureau of Forest Development shall administer and manage the reservation, in coordination with other agencies of the government, for the purposes of protecting, maintaining and improving water yield and providing a restraining mechanism for inappropriate forest exploitation and disruptive land use.

IN WITNESS HEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, in the year of Our Lord, this 13th day of May, nineteen hundred and eighty-seven.

(SGD) CORAZON C. AQUINO President of the Philippines

By the President: (SGD) JOKER P. ARROYO Executive Secretary

